data.description: Welcome home to the  pet friendly community of Boynton Lakes. This newly renovated home boasts 3 bedrooms, 2 full bathrooms, formal dining, eat-in kitchen, impact glass, newer A/C, newer tankless water heater and a brand new roof. The vaulted ceilings and open floor concept make this home the perfect space for entertaining. Step outside your screened in patio and enjoy the views of the lake from your fully fenced-in yard ready for your furry friends. Close proximity to the Publix shopping plaza.
